Configuring Community Profiles for Vlocity Cards

Ensure users see Vlocity Card Layouts on community pages by configuring user profile settings. Enable the appropriate interface, and configure custom object permissions, Visualforce page access, and Apex class access.

Disable Enhanced Profile User Interface
Enable the Original Profile Interface.

Configure Custom Object Permissions
Give access to necessary objects.

Configure Visualforce Page Access
Configure for Experience sites.

Configure Apex Class Access
Configure for Experience sites.

Configure this before users see Vlocity Card Layouts on community pages.
title: Configuring Community Profiles for Vlocity Cards
